Pleading</strong> &#8211; Just tell the other<br />
party what you are suing for Purpose of Notice is to give party<br />
notice</p>
<ol type="i">
<li>IF you DONT MEET than →<br />
12(b)(6) FAILURE TO STATE A CLAIM</li>
