<li><em><strong>Twombly<br />
and Ickball</strong></em> have thrown a lot<br />
of uncertainty into the pleading under federal rules</li>
<li>Extent to which they<br />
change a very liberal Notice Pleading is unclear</li>
<li>Pure<br />
notice Pleading WILL NOT satisfy <strong>TwomBall </strong></li>
